column2: "All patterns have been destroyed. We can no longer detect the entity. Great work!"
"Now then, for our report. There is no immediate danger, based on thorough research of the data you've collected, for the time being."
"The impact of this strange phenomenon to Oracle is very limited in scale. And its impact in the future, is within expected parameters."
"And without your cooperation, <%me>, none of this data would bear fruit. Thank you!"

"Now then, this wraps up our investigation, as there's no immediate concerns of this area. Should you be concerned regarding this area, you're free to continue your own investigation on the matter. But for now, thank you for your continued efforts!"
